  <brief_title>Study to Identify Adequate Biomarker to Detect Vitamin B12 Deficiency in Type 2 Diabetic Patients Treated With Metformin</brief_title>
  <official_title>Adequacy of Serum Vitamin B12 Measurement in Type 2 Diabetic Patients Treated With Metformin in Comparison to Holotranscobalamin Measurement</official_title>
